---
const personalImageAlt = "Piccoli Guido Augusto"
---

<article class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center justify-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <!-- Contenido textual -->
  <div class="flex-1 order-2 lg:order-1 space-y-6">
    <!-- Header con estadÃ­sticas -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-indigo-950/30 dark:to-purple-950/30 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm border border-indigo-100/50 dark:border-indigo-900/30">
      <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        About Me
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">+2</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Years experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">10+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Technologies</div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">3+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Projects</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contenido principal -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <div class="bg-white/40 dark:bg-gray-800/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200/30 dark:border-gray-700/30">
        <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
          My name is <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Guido Augusto Piccoli</strong>, 
          a developer with a passion for creating innovative digital solutions. I currently work as an 
          <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">IT Technician at Sanatorio Santa Fe</strong>, 
          where I combine web application development with comprehensive technical support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/40 dark:bg-gray-800/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200/30 dark:border-gray-700/30">
        <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
          In my current role, I develop internal web tools using 
          <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, PHP, and Python</strong>, 
          while managing technological infrastructure and providing technical support. This experience has allowed me 
          to develop a comprehensive perspective of the application lifecycle, from development to implementation and maintenance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/40 dark:bg-gray-800/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200/30 dark:border-gray-700/30">
        <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
          My experience spans modern technologies like 
          <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">React, React Native, Node.js, MySQL, and Firebase</strong>, 
          with expertise in frameworks like <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Symfony</strong> 
          and design tools like <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Tailwind CSS</strong>. 
          I also handle database tools like <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Navicat</strong> 
          for data analysis and reporting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-indigo-950/20 dark:to-purple-950/20 rounded-xl p-6 border border-indigo-100/50 dark:border-indigo-900/20">
        <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">
          I am constantly exploring new technologies and methodologies to create more efficient solutions. 
          My focus is on writing clean code, implementing scalable architectures, and optimizing performance, 
          always with the goal of providing the best possible user experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Badges de tecnologÃ­as -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      {["React", "PHP", "Python", "MySQL", "Tailwind", "Bootstrap"].map(tech => (
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 text-sm font-medium rounded-full border border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-800">
          {tech}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Imagen mejorada -->
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 order-1 lg:order-2">
    <div class="relative group">
      <!-- Anillo gradiente animado -->
      <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200 animate-pulse"></div>
      
      <!-- Imagen -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img 
          width="280" 
          height="280" 
          src="/yo.webp" 
          alt={personalImageAlt} 
          class="relative w-64 h-64 lg:w-80 lg:h-80 object-cover rounded-full shadow-2xl transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 ring-4 ring-white/70 dark:ring-gray-800/70"
          style="object-position: 50% 50%"
        />
        
        <!-- Indicador de estado -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Badge flotante -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              ðŸ’» Full Stack Developer
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>